Nutrient data for: ALMOND CRUNCHY HONEY OATS CEREAL, UPC: 078742181509
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

DEGERMED YELLOW CORN MEAL, WHOLE GRAIN WHEAT, GRANOLA CLUSTERS (WHOLE GRAIN ROLLED OATS, BROWN SUGAR, WHOLE GRAIN WHEAT FLAKES, CORN SYRUP, OAT FLOUR, HONEY, CANOLA OIL, CARAMEL [COLOR], NATURAL FLAVOR, MALTODEXTRIN, MIXED TOCOPHEROLS [PRESERVATIVE]), SUGAR, ALMONDS. CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF EACH OF THE FOLLOWING: SALT, BARLEY MALT EXTRACT, CORN SYRUP, HONEY, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, CINNAMON. VITAMINS AND MINERALS: VITAMIN C (ASCORBIC ACID, SODIUM ASCORBATE), IRON (FERROUS FUMARATE, FERRIC ORTHOPHOSPHATE), VITAMIN A PALMITATE, CALCIUM CARBONATE, NIACINAMIDE, VITAMIN B2 (RIBOFLAVIN), VITAMIN B1 (THIAMINE MONONITRATE), VITAMIN B6 (PYRIDOXINE HYDROCHLORIDE), VITAMIN D (CHOLECALCIFEROL), FOLIC ACID, VITAMIN B12 (CYANOCOBALAMIN), PANTOTHENATE, BHT ADDED TO PACKAGING TO HELP PRESERVE FRESHNESS.
